Notes: TSU jumps out to 16-4 lead in 8 minutes of game ... SBU responds with a 16-2
run in next 5 min. to take 20-18 lead ... After being down 2 at half, TSU has
16-5 run midway through 2nd half over 6 minute period for 58-50 lead and did
not look back ... TSU's first win over SBU in 11 tries (1999-2000 season)
